  "detailed_description": "WAB What A Ball - A short but intense different kind of ball racing game. Follow Blue's adventure running against MORE THAN 600 Balls racing together. Run up to 300 Km/h. It's a very challenging and hardcore game, Be Ball, Be Blue, Be Brave.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEnjoy this epic story about Blue, get a higher score and find extra bonuses when you finish the story. In this one-player game, you will find beautiful minimalistic stages full of colour. And don't forget to put the sound on.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEasy controls: WASD to move (don't hold keys), Space to Jump, Mouse to turn view.",
  "about_the_game": "WAB What A Ball - A short but intense different kind of ball racing game. Follow Blue's adventure running against MORE THAN 600 Balls racing together. Run up to 300 Km/h. It's a very challenging and hardcore game, Be Ball, Be Blue, Be Brave.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEnjoy this epic story about Blue, get a higher score and find extra bonuses when you finish the story. In this one-player game, you will find beautiful minimalistic stages full of colour. And don't forget to put the sound on.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEasy controls: WASD to move (don't hold keys), Space to Jump, Mouse to turn view.",
